data.description: If you're looking for a commercial property that has it all, then this one is definitely worth considering! With a 3 bedroom log home, a 3 bedroom apartment, and 4 pole barns, 2 offices and there's plenty of space for your business operations, as well as room for you and your employees to live comfortably. 1 hour from Indianapolis, 12 miles from Lafayette, IN, 80 Miles from Chicago and 400 Miles from St Louis.  The pole barns vary in size insulated with 220 electricity with the largest measuring in at 63 x 25.4 feet, and the smallest at 27 x 17.3 feet. There's even a 16 x 7 oversized 1 car garage workshop included, so you'll have a designated space to work on any projects or repairs that need to be done.  The showroom/office is also quite spacious, measuring in at 39.6 x 14.9 feet. This area would be perfect for meeting with clients or customers, or even for displaying any products or merchandise that you might be selling.  Overall, this commercial property has a lot to offer, and with so much space and versatility, it could be the perfect fit for a wide range of businesses. So if you're in the market for a new location for your company, be sure to check this one out!  Washer & Dryer not included. Subject to seller finding suitable housing.
